        "id": "5AF528C1-B72F-4122-A616-D114ECE40D35",
        "title": "Alcatraz Agave Trail",
        "description": "Check out the Agave Trail on the southern side of the island. Get a sense of Alcatraz's lesser known natural beauty by experiencing the flora and fauna of the Rock, home to many a feathered friend. Bird life and enviable views of the city make the Agave Trail a great alternative or addition to the main tour. The trail is open when the birds are not nesting, typically from about mid October to mid January.",
