        "title": "Alcatraz Guard Tower",
        "description": "The Guard Tower was the last line for guards to secure the island. If the men on duty saw or heard anything unusual, they would sound the alarm that went out over the whole island. Long hours in the tower meant that it had to be equipped with all the necessary facilities.",
