        "title": "Alcatraz Parade Ground",
        "description": "The Parade Grounds are an open area on the south end of Alcatraz that host surprisingly few parades. It's an excellent spot for a selfie with an awesome view of the skyline of San Francisco. Turn around, and you have the lighthouse and warden's residence for a backdrop.",
