        "title": "Alcatraz Power Plant",
        "description": "Because of its geography, Alcatraz poses unique challenges when it comes to power and sustainability. The Golden Gate National Recreation Area has taken these challenges head-on and developed several ways to improve efficiency and limit energy expenditure. Be it water usage, garbage management or carbon emissions from electricity production or transportation, we are addressing the problems.",
